1. Sector and country segment performance will be tracked individually and not as an overall portfolio;  
2. Stock additions and/or deletions will occur only once a month;  
3. Each country and sector segment performance will be tracked in USD terms (absolute and relative) for the past month and year to date;  
4. Relative performance will be tracked for each country and sector against MSCI ASEAN;  
5. Country and sector teams have the option to have no stock mentioned within their segment; and  
6. Minimum daily trading value of US\(1 million (based on 1-3 months' average).
